Ratas added that it is important to think about all those who have not had a father to be friends with.
It is our duty to strive in everyday life, politics and our actions with all our hearts to make sure that they always feel our care, strength, understanding.
Father of the Year Tiit, added scientist and father of four Arvo Tuvikene is just such a man, who has warmth for everyone.
He is praised by family members, friends, colleagues and supervisees.
Son Mikk says that his father is a model father, who has inspired children to act and decide, but also taught responsibility.
He is very affectionate, very-very affectionate person and he is also a very interesting person, his stories are very interesting to listen to.
